78587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BhA4NCfyJxsig0WsWQbjFwyd9Rk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/64A7RNEWERHILF4EUOPKSHK7OM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBhA4NCfyJxsig0WsWQbjFwyd9Rk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F64A7RNEWERHILF4EUOPKSHK7OM.jpg&h=93bb192e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港第四波疫情持續，各種防疫措施影響市民，冠域商業及經濟研究中心主任關焯照以衞生署本地感染個案（不包括輸入個案）數據編製疫情指數，分析自11月初爆發的第四波疫情，指「轉勢點」已出現，認為本地疫情似已露出一線曙光。<br />\n<br />\n「接觸點」出現代表每天平均確診宗數增幅見頂<br />\n<br />\n關焯照指從疫情爆發至完結，每天的總確診人數會出現一個S形走勢，即疫情爆發初期，每天新增確診病例宗數急速上升，但經過一段時間後，確診宗數的增加速度開始放緩，因為公共衞生部門會推出抗疫措施，例如社交隔離甚至封城；當確診宗數的上升速度由增加變為減少，過了該「轉勢點」，疫情便可以被視為初步露出曙光。<br />\n<br />\n但要確認疫情受控，要視乎「接觸點」在何時出現，他指出，「接觸點」代表每天平均確診宗數的增幅已見頂，可預期總確診宗數也很快見頂。<br />\n<br />\n第三波8.19現「接觸點」錄26確診 源頭不明個案急跌<br />\n<br />\n關焯照以第二波疫情為例，「轉勢點」為3月27日，「接觸點」為4月9日；而第三波疫情「轉勢點」在7月26日出現，「接觸點」為8月19日。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，本港7月初開始爆發第三波疫情，最高峰是7月30日錄得149宗個案；自8月3日一周起確診個案開始下跌，但速度緩慢，中間更曾出現反彈，直至8月19日錄得26宗確診個案，是自7月16日以來首次少於30宗；源頭不明個案比例則由高峰期達四成至五成，在8月中下跌至兩至三成。<br />\n<br />\n政府專家顧問許樹昌當時表示，若再沒有大型群組爆發，確診個案有望回落至單位數，便可開始放寬社交距離措施。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7n9XKX4UZX-aS8Vz-omqvGrnrKA=/802x796/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PNWULY7WZZCCHEM2F7F63SYRCA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7n9XKX4UZX-aS8Vz-omqvGrnrKA%3D%2F802x796%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPNWULY7WZZCCHEM2F7F63SYRCA.JPG&h=97ca0be1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據數據，學者指第四波疫情已過了「轉勢點」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vM5l73tauA4ccva1PDk6ElUDxkE=/802x804/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PBE2B5UIKJC6XKKF6TA65UB4PQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvM5l73tauA4ccva1PDk6ElUDxkE%3D%2F802x804%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPBE2B5UIKJC6XKKF6TA65UB4PQ.JPG&h=57a19799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二波疫情「接觸點」為4月9日，之後逐漸緩和。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eFAFFgAVdJQayJYIr2W2FyLr4K8=/802x812/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R4GAMFL55VBVDNDQBGEGTN2QDM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeFAFFgAVdJQayJYIr2W2FyLr4K8%3D%2F802x812%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR4GAMFL55VBVDNDQBGEGTN2QDM.JPG&h=dbefd143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三波疫情「轉勢點」為7月26日，當日有26宗確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n第四波12.3已現「轉勢點」 料本周內見「接觸點」<br />\n<br />\n而按關焯照編制的疫情指數，以11月1日為第四波疫情開始起計，在12月3日已出現「轉勢點」，截至今日（12月13日）即爆發第43日，尚未出現「接觸點」，不過他認為本地疫情已露出一線曙光。<br />\n<br />\n參考其編制的疫情指數，第二波疫情「轉勢點」及「接觸點」相隔14日，第三波疫情相距25日，第四波「轉勢點」出現至今為第11日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/QX7USM4ZEVARJHCMSJTOECZNEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FQX7USM4ZEVARJHCMSJTOECZNEE%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725P2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=3112c984\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FQX7USM4ZEVARJHCMSJTOECZNEE%2F&h=b0971f31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/QX7USM4ZEVARJHCMSJTOECZNEE/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:07:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">居然真係出自關Sir，好失望！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今鋪香港其實唔係咁Model！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fd45e74dc6d8a81d7b70907d2e469a51c897400b","tid":2324152,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:07:54.000Z","msg":"學者有冇返過工"},{"pid":"d330c223382b4066e1133e97abcae1e906b8e612","tid":2324152,"uid":115129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:08:01.000Z","msg":"Sample size太小<br />\n得2次做案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋次次一定差唔多既咩<br />\n你唔比十次係依個位轉勢 第十一次就死都唔轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb8452d8f2f92c468cdd33fdb55e837efc6d18a","tid":2324152,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:08:21.000Z","msg":"即係有排要守<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffd009bb3af8842a38f5855e65c0d90b223588d","tid":2324152,"uid":36135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:08:36.000Z","msg":"專家食屎喇<br />\n依家有疫苗就仆出嚟做樂觀撚收光環<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50595783580b21fa0b23cea41af274258184da9","tid":2324152,"uid":176469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"學咩者，Google咗依條友，根本就係一個圖表撚用經濟學同股票嘅角度去分析疫情，九唔搭八。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578ceb1ae5eb4b6729e31d184d160b664f549590","tid":2324152,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T01:09:37.000Z","msg":"好掛住綠衫大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786539374c48d455d6a5d711bd75d8291197c1f5","tid":2324152,"uid":176469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ffcc9b4355f37ff4c942b3fca96456399fdb02f","tid":2324152,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dis